<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Game Results</title>
    <style>
      /* Basic styles */
      body {
        font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
        color: #2f2f2f;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: justify;
      }
      a {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      table {
        font-size: 18px;
        border: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }
      .fw-bold {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #202020;
      }
      /* Container styles */
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      /* Button styles */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        background-color: #5d91e8;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #234683;
        transform: translateY(-3px);
      }
      /* Background styles */
      .background {
        background-image: url("https://i.imgur.com/jQQoX9E.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: -1;
        filter: brightness(0.7);
      }
      /* Footer styles */
      .footer {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #4485fd;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 60px 0px;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-top: 34px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer h4 {
        margin: auto 0px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      /* Media queries */
      @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          padding: 30px;
        }
        h1 {
          font-size: 28px;
        }
        p {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button {
          padding: 12px 24px;
          margin-top: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="background"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Hello, <%= userName %>.</h1>
      <p>
        Thank you for participating in the
        <span class="fw-bold"><%= game %></span> on Globeventnub. We value your
        effort and contribution in fostering a vibrant Afrobeat fan community.
        Your result and details of the event's ticket are shown below:
      </p>
      <table>
        <% for (var i = 0; i < result.length; i++) { %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= result[i].title %></td>
          <td><%= result[i].score %></td>
        </tr>
        <% } %>
        <tr>
          <td>Event name:</td>
          <td><%= eventName %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Event date:</td>
          <td><%= eventDate %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Ticket type:</td>
          <td><%= ticketType %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>
        Stay tuned as winners will be contacted via email at the end of the
        game. You could be one of them!
      </p>
      <p>
        As we continue to enhance the fan experience on Globeventnub, we invite
        you to explore our platform for more thrilling opportunities to connect
        with your favorite Afrobeat artists. Your enthusiasm serves as an
        inspiration to us, and we are committed to providing you with even more
        unforgettable moments in the future.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or require assistance, our dedicated support
        team is here to help. Please don't hesitate to reach out to us via
        support@globeventnub.com, and we will be more than happy to assist you.
      </p>
      <div class="footer">
        <h4>Eventnub</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
